HEADWORD: Clinoid
<hw>Cli"noid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>kli`nh</grk> bed + <ets>-oid</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
